# SmartStudy Hub - Environment Configuration

# Google Gemini AI API Key (for intelligent chatbot)
# Get your free API key from: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Go to https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
# 2. Sign in with your Google account
# 3. Click "Create API Key"
# 4. Copy the API key
# 5. Replace "your_api_key_here" above with your actual API key
# 6. Save this file

# Note: The chatbot will work in fallback mode without API key,
# but with API key it becomes truly intelligent!
